OL,3,CClimate change and underinvestment
OL,4,Cblamed for NI's pothole problem
OL,6,FAn additional #1million has been
OL,7,Fallocated to repair potholes on
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland's roads,
OL,9,FInfrastructure Minister John O'Dowd
OL,10,Fhas said.
OL,12,FThere were an estimated 110,000
OL,13,Fpotholes across the region, according
OL,14,Fto government data analysed by
OL,15,FCompareNI.com last month.
OL,17,FMr O'Dowd said the funding is to be
OL,18,Fspent in the coming weeks before the
OL,19,Fend of this financial year.
