OL,3,CClimate change and underinvestment
OL,4,Cblamed for NI's pothole problem
OL,6,FHe said currently around 7,000
OL,7,Fpotholes a month are fixed, but more
OL,8,Fneeds to be done to repair Northern
OL,9,FIreland's road network.
OL,11,FThe minister blamed underinvestment
OL,12,Fand the impact of climate change for
OL,13,Fsevere damage to some roads.
OL,15,F"This extra allocation will go some
OL,16,Fway to address the roads with the most
OL,17,Fsignificant need," he said.
OL,19,F"Unfortunately, a number of factors
OL,20,Fhave recently made the situation worse.
