OL,3,CClimate change and underinvestment
OL,4,Cblamed for NI's pothole problem
OL,6,F"For the last decade the department
OL,7,Fhas been operating in a challenging
OL,8,Ffinancial position due to British
OL,9,FGovernment cuts and austerity which
OL,10,Fhas had an impact on road maintenance
OL,11,Factivities and the overall condition
OL,12,Fof the road network.
OL,14,F"Add to that, the impact of climate
OL,15,Fchange, with the wettest October in
OL,16,Fover 153 years of records, which
OL,17,Fcaused severe damage to some roads
OL,18,Facross the north."
